### Foods API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

# Search Foods (public)
GET {{baseURL}}/foods/search?q=rice

###

# Get Foods by Vendor (public)
GET {{baseURL}}/foods/vendor/vendor_id_here

###

# Create Food (vendor only)
POST {{baseURL}}/foods
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "vendorId": "vendor_id_here",
  "name": "Jollof Rice",
  "unit": "plates",
  "price": 1500,
  "category": "Main",
  "prepTime": 25
}

###

# Update Food (vendor only)
PATCH {{baseURL}}/foods/food_id_here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "price": 1800,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

# Delete Food (vendor only)
DELETE {{baseURL}}/foods/food_id_here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}